               <p>OLD COURT. Thursday, January 2, 1834.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Alderson.</p>
               <p>183. 
               
                  <persName id="t18340102-2-defend123" type="defendantName">
                     GEORGE 
                     ALLUM
                  <interp inst="t18340102-2-defend123" type="surname" value="ALLUM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340102-2-defend123" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>
