               Transported for Life
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>JONES. Aged 20. <rs id="t18340102-2-verdict20" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340102-2-verdict20" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340102-2-verdict20" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18340102-2-punish21" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340102-2-punish21" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340102-2-defend130 t18340102-2-punish21"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Jones recommended to mercy, believing him to have acted under the influence of others. There was another indictment against Allum and Preston.</p>
